text.tspan: Tick Tock, where time dances with childhood
dreams. Here, memories of laughter and play inter
twine with the passage of time, creating a canvas
As kids, time was like a slinky, twisting and turning
with each new adventure. Our toys were more than
objectsthey were gateways to magical worlds,
This website is a tribute to those cherished moments,
with graphics inspired by the playful motion of a
slinky. Here, time is not just seconds ticking by, but
the joy of discovery and the thrill of exploration.
After all, as the poem my mother sang to me re
minds us, "twinkle twinkle little stars, up above where
we are," time may pass, but the memories we hold
dear will always shine bright in the constellation of
